description:
Location of reefs close to coast of Namibia.
Source: Orthophotos 2001 - 2002 made by Airborne Laser Solutions for Ministry of Lands & Resettlement (MLR) which cover about 300 to 500 m of area offshore. Method: Digitised from colour orthophotos Surveyor General and topographic maps 1:50K
name: Namibia: location of reefs close to the coast
